<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nisa tumna khel lam achun,
 Mei kaihna van khelah;
 Zan aksi vakna khel achun,
 Chunglam ah In ka nei.

[V2]
 Khuta sakloh, van In nuom chuh,
 Kei din guotsa ahi;
 Pathien Angel la sakna chuh,
 Zie chuh ka In ahi.

[V3]
 2. Natna leh buoina khel achun,
 Damsung haksa khel ah;
 Phat zatchuom tak lohna achun,
 Ka In nuom chuh a um.

[V4]
 3. Thihna tui kinawk khel lamah,
 Zan thim khel lam achun;
 Lunggil kipak takin ka en,
 Van chunga In vak chuh.

[V5]
 4. Ka gitloh, lungkham lauhna te,
 Ka nung sawn vek tai tun;
 Kumsawt a chunglam van In ah,
 Lal Krista tawh cheng kau.</lyrics>
<title>A HOME ON HIGH</title>
<hymn_number>379</hymn_number>
</song>